{"tid":2201149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗無視國際呼籲 處決涉嫌謀殺摔跤手","createTime":"2020-09-13T14:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T16:54:58.000Z","uid":295230,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dad001045064d5750e6e8e089c7eb8cb02185081","tid":2201149,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"伊朗冠軍級摔跤手阿夫卡里(Navid Afkari)被指在兩年前的反政府示威中刺死保安員，伊朗無視國際要求赦免的呼籲，周六處決阿夫卡里。<br />\n<br />\n阿夫卡里被控在2018年一場反政府示威中，殺害自來水公司保安員蒂爾克曼。伊朗國營電視台上周曾播出片段，顯示阿夫卡里重組案情時，招認用刀殺人，兇器藏在家中，並顯示他曾書面承認犯案。但據他家人透露，阿夫卡里曾辯稱自己因經不起虐打才被迫認罪，他的律師亦表示找不出他殺人的證據，惟伊朗司法機關未有接納阿夫卡里的說法。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧形容伊朗的做法是對人類尊嚴作出肆無忌憚攻擊，予以最強烈譴責。國際奧委會對阿夫卡里被處決感到震驚；代表全球8.5萬名運動員的世界運動員總會強調事件可怕，協會早前稱，如果伊朗堅持行刑，應該將伊朗逐出世界體育之中。"},{"pid":"d24603b93e748f0d2ee750d0c41c7ebbe89da882","tid":2201149,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rEZU4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rEZU4t.jpg&h=21b2216d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aa3c2af78cf3a9fbde9dbbc76af976f8346c6e5","tid":2201149,"uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邪惡軸心"},{"pid":"4eeff2d1e55d853d834ffbd337f754f0f21b36a7","tid":2201149,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/NUFDIran/status/1304982126236925952?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNUFDIran%2Fstatus%2F1304982126236925952%3Fs%3D19&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8DrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=18b9c57d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNUFDIran%2F